
Activities - entity type in Drupal
   Start Date
   End Date
   Video Time
   EventID
   ProjectID - can be derived from Event
   UserID - email address
   Description - 255 chars?
   Content - infinite characters
     
   Function:Activity
      msg: chat, question, poll, notify, notes
      act: play, pause, enter, leave, elapsed
           volume_up, volumn_down
           full_screen, normal_screen
           cc_on, cc_off
      alm: on, off
      cod: warning, error, debug
   
